Output demo.mp4

Set Width 1320
Set Height 600
Set FontSize 13
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Framerate 60

Hide
Type "./matri.sh"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Show

Type "echo 'hello from the matrix'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 2s

Type "ls -la"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 5s

Type "git status"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 3s

Type "glods"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 3s

Type "grep MATRISH_ matri.sh"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 3s

Type "claude"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 3s

Type "Tell me about this repo"
Enter

Sleep 30s
